test_large_range:
assert [7, 8] == [9]
  At index 0 diff: 7 != 9
  Left contains one more item: 8
  Full diff:
  - [9]
  + [7, 8]
test_even_range:
assert [7, 8] == [18]
  At index 0 diff: 7 != 18
  Left contains one more item: 8
  Full diff:
  - [18]
  + [7, 8]
test_zero_range:
assert [7, 8] == []
  Left contains 2 more items, first extra item: 7
  Full diff:
  - []
  + [7, 8]
